Now let’s generate a table that summarises some descriptives

data_percentages <- all_data_stats %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = subfield_groups, values_from = "Number", c("Real_Stage", "Number")) 

data_summary <- gt(data_percentages) %>%
  cols_label(Real_Stage = "Open Data Practice") %>%
      cols_move(columns = c(Development, Social, Cognition, Other),
    after = `Real_Stage`) %>%
  opt_table_font("Times New Roman") %>%
  cell_text(color = "black")
